** Heading +Sym
** CalculiX steady thermal template
** Rendered by AI-FEA Solver Agent from SimPlan parameters.
**
** Variables (Jinja2):
**   mesh_include         — path to .inp mesh file
**   material_name        — e.g. "Steel"
**   thermal_conductivity — W/(m.K)
**   specific_heat        — J/(kg.K) (optional)
**   temp_node_set        — node set for fixed temperature
**   temperature          — fixed temperature value (K or C)
**   load_node_set        — node set for heat flux
**   heat_flux            — concentrated flux value (W)
**
*INCLUDE, INPUT={{ mesh_include }}
**
** MATERIAL
*MATERIAL, NAME={{ material_name }}
*CONDUCTIVITY
{{ thermal_conductivity | default(50.0) }}
{% if specific_heat %}
*SPECIFIC HEAT
{{ specific_heat }}
{% endif %}
**
** SOLID SECTION (assumes single part)
*SOLID SECTION, ELSET=Eall, MATERIAL={{ material_name }}
**
** BOUNDARY CONDITIONS (DOF 11 = Temperature)
{% if temp_node_set and temperature is not none %}
*BOUNDARY
{{ temp_node_set }}, 11, 11, {{ temperature }}
{% endif %}
**
** STEP
*STEP
*HEAT TRANSFER, STEADY STATE
**
** LOADS (Concentrated heat flux on nodes, DOF 11)
{% if load_node_set and heat_flux is not none %}
*CFLUX
{{ load_node_set }}, 11, {{ heat_flux }}
{% endif %}
**
** OUTPUT
*NODE FILE
NT
*EL FILE
HFL
**
*END STEP
